com.interpss.core.aclf.contingency

Interface OutageBranch

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BranchRef<AclfBranch>, com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, NameTag, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    OutageBranchImpl

    public interface OutageBranch
extends BranchRef<AclfBranch>
    A representation of the model object 'Outage Branch'. Outage branch for branch contingency analysis. The reference AclfBranch could be inactive. Also, an outage branch could be set inactive, if, for example, it connects two island buses.

    The following features are supported:

    • Island Number
    • Outage Type
    See Also:
    ContingencyPackage.getOutageBranch()

      • getIslandNumber

        int getIslandNumber()
        Returns the value of the 'Island Number' attribute. island number of the outage branch, range [0 .. n-1]. If an outage branch connects to two island buses, these two buses should be in the same island subnetwork.
        Returns:
        the value of the 'Island Number' attribute.
